%F A007378 a(3*2^k + j) = 4*2^k + 3j/2 + |j|/2, k>=0, -2^k <= j < 2^k. - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Feb 23 2003
%F A007378 a(2*n+1) = a(n+1)+a(n), a(2*n) = 2*a(n). a(n) = n+A060973(n). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Mar 01 2003
